    "body": "@churik so I checked and the layout of this component was changed in delete message pr ([here](https://github.com/status-im/status-react/commit/8ec46a0d78b7a6e28286e42ff9af60799162b3c0)).\r\n\r\nAs far as I see, we have it used for next types of messages:\r\n1. regular text message 1-1 chat/private group: edit/reply/copy/pin/delete for incoming, reply/copy/pin for outgoing\r\n2. regular text message in pub chat/communities: edit/reply/copy/delete fro incoming, reply/copy for outgoing\r\n3. image in 1-1 chat/private group/communities: reply/save for both cases\r\n4. sticker 1-1 chat: View Details for incoming (currently also has that `!` mark)\r\n5. status text message: copy for both\r\n\r\nSo the question is: in which cases we want to align them vertically and have an icon, in which cases we want to align them horizontally. Just to fix it for all cases. ",
